description: Defines data models for stock quotes and market alerts, including classes Quote and MarketAlert with factory methods for mock data generation.

classes.name: Quote
classes.description: Represents a stock quote with symbol, price, change, changePercent, timestamp, and signal.

classes.name: MarketAlert
classes.description: Represents a market alert with title, description, and timestamp.

methods.name: Quote.mock
methods.description: Generates a mock Quote instance with random data based on a symbol.

methods.name: MarketAlert.mock
methods.description: Generates a mock MarketAlert instance with a given title.
